column5: ...if you don't mind watching snow falling on April 27th Crazy weather eh ?? LOL
Snowed and now blowing like crazy, 70k wind.
Yeah, it's breezy over this way too. I planned on building some new front steps today but I think I'll put it off for awhile.
Not impressed at all, muddy laneway was just starting to be passable for cars and we have family "Easter" dinner tomorrow.
Wayne, you definitely have it worse then we do down here, lol. I wonder how many guys are fishing trout opener today

The rivers and creeks I seen well,I wasn't fishing them.LOL  What was here this morning is pretty much gone   The Barrie marina has put in new docks at the launch. Looks like they built these ones right this time. Full metal pontoons and a ramp that will work with water levels.
LOL, even a chance of snow overnight here in the tropics! It's been a strange spring here too, 70f one day 40's the next.
Snowfall only surprises me from mid-June to mid-September lol
